  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join in with the fun as you’re given the job of returning errant birds to their nests by the farm Rooster, the catch is, you've got to do this in the most efficient way possible.  Fortunately, the lazy birds are rather round and roll easily at the slightest touch, bouncing upright when they come to a stop. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/ef4db4cdef0b460e21a55fcbe5547b1b.poster.avif?t=1765064876\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/ef4db4cdef0b460e21a55fcbe5547b1b.webm?t=1765064876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/ef4db4cdef0b460e21a55fcbe5547b1b.mp4?t=1765064876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rolling each lost bird to its correct type of nest completes the day, but watch out, the Rooster will be watching your every move, take too many and he may fail you!  Luckily, he lets you in on a little secret early into your SokoFarming career allowing you to undo moves to correct your mistakes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/f5000850d3231232d3b01d4461ae1bf2.poster.avif?t=1765064876\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/f5000850d3231232d3b01d4461ae1bf2.webm?t=1765064876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/f5000850d3231232d3b01d4461ae1bf2.mp4?t=1765064876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move from farm to farm as the seasons progress with each new location presenting our SokoFarmers with increasingly baffling puzzles as Chickens, Ducks, Geese and even the occasional log or two join in making everything just that little bit more mind bogglingly great. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/ecf5b9703ac634c2936d8987d1eb7452.poster.avif?t=1765064876\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/ecf5b9703ac634c2936d8987d1eb7452.webm?t=1765064876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/ecf5b9703ac634c2936d8987d1eb7452.mp4?t=1765064876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No-one said being a SokoFarmer was a push over, but it sure is fun! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 Sokoban puzzles to master </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customisable player characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play across all four seasons in one game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each new season adds additional puzzle complexity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple bird and nest types for increased difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single axis obstacles to add to the fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move count targets to promote re-playability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute, cosy graphics and animation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bouncy, fun sound effects and music</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join in with the fun as you’re given the job of returning errant birds to their nests by the farm Rooster, the catch is, you've got to do this in the most efficient way possible.  Fortunately, the lazy birds are rather round and roll easily at the slightest touch, bouncing upright when they come to a stop. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/ef4db4cdef0b460e21a55fcbe5547b1b.poster.avif?t=1765064876\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/ef4db4cdef0b460e21a55fcbe5547b1b.webm?t=1765064876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/ef4db4cdef0b460e21a55fcbe5547b1b.mp4?t=1765064876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rolling each lost bird to its correct type of nest completes the day, but watch out, the Rooster will be watching your every move, take too many and he may fail you!  Luckily, he lets you in on a little secret early into your SokoFarming career allowing you to undo moves to correct your mistakes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/f5000850d3231232d3b01d4461ae1bf2.poster.avif?t=1765064876\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/f5000850d3231232d3b01d4461ae1bf2.webm?t=1765064876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/f5000850d3231232d3b01d4461ae1bf2.mp4?t=1765064876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move from farm to farm as the seasons progress with each new location presenting our SokoFarmers with increasingly baffling puzzles as Chickens, Ducks, Geese and even the occasional log or two join in making everything just that little bit more mind bogglingly great. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/ecf5b9703ac634c2936d8987d1eb7452.poster.avif?t=1765064876\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/ecf5b9703ac634c2936d8987d1eb7452.webm?t=1765064876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775040/extras/ecf5b9703ac634c2936d8987d1eb7452.mp4?t=1765064876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No-one said being a SokoFarmer was a push over, but it sure is fun! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 Sokoban puzzles to master </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customisable player characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play across all four seasons in one game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each new season adds additional puzzle complexity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple bird and nest types for increased difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single axis obstacles to add to the fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move count targets to promote re-playability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute, cosy graphics and animation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bouncy, fun sound effects and music</p></li></ul>",
